      <title>随着美国控制收紧，韩国对中国水槽的芯片出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/south-korea-s-chip-exports-to-china-sink-as-us-controls-tighten</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，韩国对中国的半导体出口暴跌，加深了人们对美国关税已经威胁到的全球需求冷却的担忧，因为华盛顿加大了对北京技术供应的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/south-korea-s-chip-exports-to-china-sink-as-us-controls-tighten</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 02:05:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪称赞与特朗普的关系，这些联系正在受到关税威胁的测试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/modi-praises-ties-with-trump-that-are-now-being-tested-by-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪（Narendra Modi）对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示赞赏，这是一个有勇气的人，强调了牢固的个人纽带，现在由美国总统的关税计划进行了考验，其中还包括南亚国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/modi-praises-ties-with-trump-that-are-now-being-tested-by-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 01:59:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本总理Ishiba的支持暴跌给立法者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/japan-s-ishiba-support-plunges-in-polls-after-voucher-blunder</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对日本总理史密斯（Shigeru Ishiba）的支持下降了，因为他承认向新当选的立法者分发了价值数百美元的购物券，这使一个少数族裔政府已经努力在今年夏天努力通过预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/japan-s-ishiba-support-plunges-in-polls-after-voucher-blunder</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 01:19:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Anwar联盟合作伙伴需要PMS的10年限制：Malay Mail</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/anwar-coalition-partner-wants-10-year-limits-for-pms-malay-mail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来邮政报道，民主党行动党是统治联盟中议会最多的席位，希望政府将修改联邦宪法，将总理限制为最多10年的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/anwar-coalition-partner-wants-10-year-limits-for-pms-malay-mail</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 00:19:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>看门狗说，英国必须尝试了解移民工人的激增。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/uk-must-try-to-understand-migrant-worker-surge-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名官方监督机构说，英国政府应立即采取措施确定是什么推动了工人签证的爆炸，这强调了该国有争议的移民辩论中心的计划缺乏监督。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/uk-must-try-to-understand-migrant-worker-surge-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国轴监管机构，目标是经济增长驱动器的福利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/uk-axes-regulators-targets-welfare-in-economic-growth-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府将废除更多的业务监管机构，并减少福利支出，以推动停滞的经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/uk-axes-regulators-targets-welfare-in-economic-growth-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/half-a-million-uk-homebuyers-rush-to-beat-tax-rise-survey-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据房地产网站RightMove的数据，超过50万英国的购房者正试图在4月初关闭税收减免大满贯之前将交易结合起来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/half-a-million-uk-homebuyers-rush-to-beat-tax-rise-survey-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>持续不必担心市场，呼吁更正健康</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/bessent-says-he-s-not-worried-about-market-corrections-healthy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）是前对冲基金经理，他说，由于美国试图重塑其经济政策，他并不担心最近的经济下滑，从股票市场擦掉了数万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/bessent-says-he-s-not-worried-about-market-corrections-healthy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 15:22:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普驱逐了数百名敌人的法院谴责法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/trump-deports-hundreds-under-enemies-act-as-court-rebukes-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府表示，它逮捕了委内瑞拉的特伦·德·阿拉古亚帮派成千上万的据称成员，送往萨尔瓦多，即使联邦法官下令停止一些驱逐出境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/trump-deports-hundreds-under-enemies-act-as-court-rebukes-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 15:19:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>我们发誓要“毫不留情”对红海攻击的胡希斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/us-attacks-on-houthis-will-be-unrelenting-hegseth-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼负责人皮特·赫格斯斯（Pete Hegseth）周日表示，在唐纳德·赫斯斯（Pete Hegseth）下天，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统下令在中东下令新的业务后，美国对也门的军事罢工将“不屈不挠”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/us-attacks-on-houthis-will-be-unrelenting-hegseth-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 15:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
